rap"><ul id="menu-secondary" class="nav superfish"><li id="menu-item-3750" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category current-post-ancestor menu-item-3750"><a href="http://www.sharonblog.com/category/family-life-and-other-awesome-stuff/">Family, Life, and other Awesome Stuff!</a></li>
