				<h1 class="entry-title">Maple-Bacon Buttermilk Waffles &#8211; Recipe</h1>
		
		<div class="post-info"><span class="date published time" title="2011-08-01T00:01:47-0500">August 1, 2011</span>  | <span class="post-comments"><a href="http://www.sharonblog.com/maple-bacon-buttermilk-waffles-recipe/#comments">4 Comments</a></span> | <?php if(function_exists('the_views')) { the_views(); } ?>  </div><div class="post-info"></div>		<div class="entry-content">
			<div id="ph_social_share_top" class="ph_social_share_box ph_social_share_box_top"><div class="phsmc" id="phsmc_top_facebook"><a name="fb_share" type="button_count" share_url="http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sharonblog.com%2Fmaple-bacon-buttermilk-waffles-recipe%2F" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sharonblog.com%2Fmaple-bacon-buttermilk-waffles-recipe%2F&t=Maple-Bacon%20Buttermilk%20Waffles%20%26%238211%3B%20Recipe">Share</a><script src="http://static.ak.fbcdn.net/connect.php/js/FB.Share" type="text/javascript"></script></div><div class="phsmc" id="phsmc_top_twitter"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://www.sharonblog.com/maple-bacon-buttermilk-waffles-recipe/" data-count="horizontal" data-via="sharonrose">Tweet</a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script></div><div class="phsmc" id="phsmc_top_stumble"><script src="http://www.stumbleupon.com/hostedbadge.php?s=1&r=http://www.sharonblog.com/maple-bacon-buttermilk-waffles-recipe/"></script></div><div class="clear"></div></div>
