<div class="easyrecipe">
<table class="ERHDTable" border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><span class="item ERName"><span class="fn">Maple-Bacon Buttermilk Waffles &#8211; Recipe</span></span></td>
<td align="center" valign="top">
<div class="ERRatingOuter">
<div class="ERRatingInner" style="width:100%;"></div>
<div class="review hreview-aggregate"><span class="rating"><span class="average">5.0</span> from <span class="count">1</span> reviews</span></div>
</div>
</td>
<td class="ERHDPrint" valign="top">
<div class="btnERPrint">Print</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div class="ERClear"></div>
<div class="ERHead">Prep time: <span class="preptime">5 mins<span class="value-title" title="PT5M"> </span></span></div>
<div class="ERHead">Cook time: <span class="cooktime">30 mins<span class="value-title" title="PT30M"> </span></span></div>
<div class="ERHead">Total time: <span class="duration">35 mins<span class="value-title" title="PT35M"> </span></span></div>
<div class="ERIngredientsHeader">Ingredients</div>
<ul class="ingredients">
<li class="ingredient">2 cups all-purpose flour</li>
<li class="ingredient">1/4 cup sugar</li>
<li class="ingredient">1 1/2 teaspoon baking soda</li>
<li class="ingredient">1/2 teaspoon salt</li>
<li class="ingredient">1 3/4 cups buttermilk</li>
<li class="ingredient">2 eggs</li>
<li class="ingredient">6 tablespoons melted butter</li>
<li class="ingredient">1 1/2 teaspoon maple flavor (maple extract)</li>
<li class="ingredient">1 package or jar cooked real bacon pieces or bits</li>
<li class="ingredient">1 1/2 cups real maple or maple-flavored syrup</li>
</ul>
<div class="ERInstructionsHeader">Instructions</div>
<div class="instructions">
<ol>
<li class="instruction">Heat waffle maker</li>
<li class="instruction">In large bow mix flour, sugar, baking soda, and salt.</li>
<li class="instruction">In medium bowl beat buttermilk, eggs, butter, and maple flavor with wire whisk until well blended, Pour over dry ingredients. and stir until well moistened.</li>
<li class="instruction">Sprinkle about 2 teaspoons of bacon pieces over each waffle grid.</li>
<li class="instruction">Spoon batter over bacon, using amount recommended by manufacturer.</li>
<li class="instruction">Close lid of waffle maker.</li>
<li class="instruction">Bake until steaming stops, 3 to 5 minutes.</li>
<li class="instruction">Repeat with remaining bacon and batter.</li>
<li class="instruction">Serve waffles with syrup.</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="nutrition"></div>
<div class="endeasyrecipe" style="display: none;">1.2.4</div>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p></div>

